  <entry>
    <title>如何从mac系统传输文件或文件夹到Ubuntu系统</title>
    <link href="https://zhangzhongchuan.github.io/2021/05/24/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%8Emac%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%B0Ubuntu%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/"/>
    <id>https://zhangzhongchuan.github.io/2021/05/24/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BB%8Emac%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E4%BC%A0%E8%BE%93%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%B0Ubuntu%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</id>
    <published>2021-05-24T06:12:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-05-25T09:32:25.218Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="note info">    <h5>1.问题描述</h5>    <p>如何从mac系统传输文件到Ubuntu系统？</p></div><div class="note warning">    <h5>2.问题原因</h5>    <p>无</p></div><div class="note">    <h5>2.解决方法</h5>    <p>使用scp命令，方法如下：</p></div><p>2.1从本地复制到远程(Mac→Ubuntu)</p><p>传输文件(需要输入远程用户密码)：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">XXXMacBook-Pro:~ user$ scp /Users/user/testScp.txt root@192.168.1.177:/home/user</span><br><span class="line">root@192.168.1.XXX<span class="string">&#x27;s password:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">testScp.txt                                                    100%    0     0.0KB/s   00:00</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>传输目录：</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">XXXMacBook-Pro:~ user$ scp -r /Users/user/testScp root@192.168.7.177:/home/user</span><br><span class="line">root@192.168.1.XXX<span class="string">&#x27;s password:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">test1.txt                                                      100%    0     0.0KB/s   00:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">testScp.txt                                                    100%    0     0.0KB/s   00:00</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.2从远程复制到本地(Ubuntu→Mac)</p><p>传输文件：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">XXXMacBook-Pro:~ user$ scp root@192.168.1.XXX:/home/user/testScp.txt /Users/user/</span><br><span class="line">root@192.168.1.XXX<span class="string">&#x27;s passwoXXX</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">testScp.txt                                                    100%    8     5.4KB/s   00:00</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>传输目录：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">XXXMacBook-Pro:~ user$ scp -r root@192.168.1.XXX:/home/user/testScp/ /Users/user/</span><br><span class="line">root@192.168.1.XXX<span class="string">&#x27;s password:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">test1.txt                                                      100%   12     8.8KB/s   00:00</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">testScp.txt                                                    100%   24    15.1KB/s   00:00</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note unreleased">    <h5>&nbsp &nbsp4.相关参考</h5>    <p>&nbsp &nbsp</p></div><p>4.1参考于该网站<a href="https://www.runoob.com/linux/linux-comm-scp.html">www.runoob.com</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;note info&quot;&gt;
    &lt;h5&gt;1.问题描述&lt;/h5&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;如何从mac系统传输文件到Ubuntu系统？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;note warning&quot;&gt;
    &lt;h5&gt;2.问题原因&lt;/h5&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
